metadata.name: Rural Life in Afghanistan
metadata.description:
When Ever You Get Up Early In The Moring And Take A Trip To The Country Side You Feels a Special Kind Of Freshness And Positive Energy.

On 25 January 2020 
I Get Up Early In The Morning And Went To Country Side Some Where In Afghanistan. The Green Fields Were Still Having Dew Drops. I Took Off My Boots So i   Can Get The Refreshing Feelings Of Grass Having Dew Drop. Suddenly An Old Farmer Appeared In Front Of Me With A Smiling Face I Wanted To Capture That Moment .......
